						<strong>Nintendo</strong> featuring their mascot, <strong>Mario</strong>.
						Alternatively called the <strong>Super Mario Bros</strong>.
						The Super Mario games follow Mario's adventures in the fictional 
						<strong>Mushroom Kingdom</strong>.
						The player runs and jumps across platforms and atop enemies in themed levels.
						The games have simple plots, typically with Mario rescuing the kidnapped 
						<strong>Princess Peach</strong> from the primary antagonist, <strong>Bowser</strong>.
